&lt;p&gt;Please join us for the first event in the new Columbia Climate School Speaker Series, featuring &lt;strong&gt;Catherine McKenna,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;former Canadian Minister of Environment and Climate Change and current&amp;nbsp;Distinguished Visiting Fellow with the Center on Global Energy Policy, Columbia University.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The program will run from 5pm-6pm, followed by a reception from 6pm-7pm.&lt;/p&gt;
