&lt;p&gt;Brazil Seminar: &lt;strong&gt;Freedom of Speech &amp;amp; Democracy&lt;/strong&gt; in Times of Fake News&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Guest Speaker: &lt;strong&gt;Patricia Campos Mello&lt;/strong&gt;, Research Fellow, Columbia University. Columnist, Folha de S&amp;atilde;o Paulo.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
