&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Yuri I. Shevchuk&lt;/strong&gt;, Lecturer in Ukrainian at Columbia University&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Maria Sonevytsky&lt;/strong&gt;, Associate Professor of Anthropology and Music at Bard College&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Kate Tsurkan&lt;/strong&gt;, writer, editor, translator, and PhD candidate at New York University&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Moderator:&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Mark Andryczyk&lt;/strong&gt;, Associate Research Scholar and administrator of the Ukrainian Studies Program at the Harriman Institute&lt;/p&gt;
