&lt;p&gt;CUIMC Students! Ready to finish your thesis, capstone, or dissertation?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us at The Write Stuff: Write Now and finish your project off strong with help in writing, editing, and presenting your research.&amp;nbsp;In the The Write Stuff:&amp;nbsp; Oral Presentation Skills workshop, participants will hone their oral presentation skills.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;From enunciation to pitch, rate and more, this session provides a closer look at the fundamental techniques necessary to deliver one&amp;rsquo;s presentation with confidence and ease. &amp;nbsp;It includes a fun and light-hearted opportunity to practice presentation delivery and receive feedback.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;About The Write Stuff: Write Now series&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Write Stuff: Write Now series gives you tips and tools to organize, prioritize, and plan ahead to effectively write a research project. You&amp;rsquo;ll also learn&amp;nbsp;tips and tricks to improve your self-editing and oral presentation skills.&lt;/p&gt;
